data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful 2017 Parade Home is less than 5 minutes from the sports complex, and everything Youngsville has to offer! Drive up to a beautiful landscaped front. Such a great curb appeal.   Walk in to your new home and you will notice a beautiful floor plan with multiple trey ceilings, and stunning wood floors. Den offers a gas fire place. Kitchen and dining room area is an open space great for entertaining and has gas stove and granite counters, as well as breakfast sitting area at island.  Primary bedroom offers large walk-in closet, soaking tub and private shower. With the split floor plan this is a great space for privacy and relaxing. Don't forget about the great back yard that has a covered patio, landscaped yard and fully fenced. This home cannot be missed!
